168", "card_id": "Q_668020188", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《黑神话·悟空》的热度是因为游戏出彩还是宣传到位？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最初知道黑悟空是因为知道他们曾经是斗战神的开发团队，当初玩斗战神时就感觉其背景故事及剧情很惊艳，再看到黑悟空最初版的宣传片，真真的被吸引住。发售后的热度证实了不止我一人被圈粉，只是不知道大家都是被什么所吸引。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-6fa9d003d4b9d9925e361cb6540f0c3e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "124 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/668020188"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0LGF8dGIqZsHEAMaCTExMDcyNjkzNSCalMi3BjAAOGpABXIJNjY4MDIwMTg4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1727230289.673170", "card_id": "Q_667902633", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待西安石油大学教师张峰在社交媒体上发了 397 页 PDF 举报同学院两名老师学术不端？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "具体证据材料"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b07916718d83e7fe5f3a77567e51b83b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "104 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/667902633"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0LGF8dGIqZsHEAMaCTExMDcwMDcwMiCB0MG3BjAAOEVABnIJNjY3OTAyNjMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1727230289.675607", "card_id": "Q_660907063", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80